  "title": "Clinic therapist",
  "description": "<p>Aesthetic Clinic Therapist</p><p>Looking for a clinic assistant/therapist to join our family!<br /><br /><strong>Aesthetic Treatments</strong></p><ul><li>Perform non-invasive treatments such as Hydrafacial, chemical peels, and other skin therapies under supervision and training</li></ul><p><strong>Clinical Support</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare patients for procedures</li><li>Assist the doctor during aesthetic treatments</li><li>Support post-treatment care and maintain treatment room cleanliness</li></ul><p><strong>Clinic Operations</strong></p><ul><li>Carry out general administrative duties and assist with day-to-day clinic tasks</li><li>Maintain inventory, cleanliness, and compliance with hygiene standards</li></ul><p><strong>Patient Experience</strong></p><ul><li>Build rapport and foster positive, trusting relationships with patients</li><li>Provide excellent service to ensure a warm and professional clinic environment</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Minimum 1 year of experience as a Clinic Assistant or Therapist in an aesthetic clinic in Singapore or related healthcare fields.</p><p>· A positive, service-oriented attitude with excellent interpersonal skills</p><p>· Passionate about aesthetics, personal grooming, and patient care</p><p>· Able to work independently and as part of a supportive team</p><p><strong>Salary and benefits:</strong></p><p>· Attractive commission</p><p>· Regular working hours - no Sundays and pH</p><p>· Nurturing team and staff</p><p>· Career progression and training will be provided</p><p>Interested candidate, please provide the following:</p><p>1. Current/Last drawn basic salary, incentives and/or bonus</p><p>2. Notice period in your current company, email, mobile contact</p>",
